            <p class="large text-center intro-desc">
                <strong>1.</strong> No delivery fees&nbsp;&nbsp;
                <strong>2.</strong> No Taxes&nbsp;&nbsp;
                <strong>3.</strong> No Tips&nbsp;&nbsp;
                <strong>4.</strong> No waiting in lines&nbsp;&nbsp;
                <br />
                <strong>+</strong>
                <br />
                <strong>5.</strong> Premium Japanese rice dishes handcrafted by experienced Japanese chef.
                <br />
                <strong>=</strong>
